o-user-action-name=\"header.language.toggle\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-languages\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m5 8 6 6\"></path><path d=\"m4 14 6-6 2-3\"></path><path d=\"M2 5h12\"></path><path d=\"M7 2h1\"></path><path d=\"m22 22-5-10-5 10\"></path><path d=\"M14 18h6\"></path></svg><span>मराठी</span></button><a data-faro-user-action-name=\"header.cta.contact\" class=\"button button-primary button-sm desktop-cta\" href=\"/contact\">Let’s talk<!-- --> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">↗</span></a><button class=\"menu-button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Open navigation\" data-faro-user-action-name=\"header.mobile-menu.open\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 18h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 6h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><main><section class=\"page-hero\"><div class=\"page-hero-orb\"></div><div class=\"container\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><span class=\"kicker\">About Finopia</span><h1>A financial literacy company built around better decisions.</h1><p>Finopia Services was founded on a simple belief: families deserve financial conversations they can understand, participate in and act on with confidence.</p></div></section><section class=\"section\"><div class=\"container narrative-grid\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><span class=\"kicker\">Our mission</span><h2>Empower 10,000 families through financial literacy and discipline.</h2></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p class=\"large-copy\">Empower 10,000 families through financial literacy, financial discipline and informed financial decisions.</p><p>We bring education, mutual fund distribution and insurance solutions into one thoughtful ecosystem—without confusing education with advice or making promises markets cannot keep.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"section values-section\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"section-heading\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><span class=\"kicker\">How we work</span><h2>Values visible in every conversation.</h2></div><div class=\"value-grid\"><div class=\"value-card\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><h3>Clarity</h3><p>We explain before we recommend a next step.</p></div><div class=\"value-card\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-scale\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m16 16 3-8 3 8c-.87.65-1.92 1-3 1s-2.13-.35-3-1Z\"></path><path d=\"m2 16 3-8 3 8c-.87.65-1.92 1-3 1s-2.13-.35-3-1Z\"></path><path d=\"M7 21h10\"></path><path d=\"M12 3v18\"></path><path d=\"M3 7h2c2 0 5-1 7-2 2 1 5 2 7 2h2\"></path></svg><h3>Responsibility</h3><p>We stay grounded in compliance and honest expectations.</p></div><div class=\"value-card\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart-handshake\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z\"></path><path d=\"M12 5 9.04 7.96a2.17 2.17 0 0 0 0 3.08c.82.82 2.13.85 3 .07l2.07-1.9a2.82 2.82 0 0 1 3.79 0l2.96 2.66\"></path><path d=\"m18 15-2-2\"></path><path d=\"m15 18-2-2\"></path></svg><h3>Empathy</h3><p>Real financial lives are personal, nuanced and human.</p></div><div class=\"value-card\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-eye\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.062 12.348a1 1 0 0 1 0-.696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1 19.876 0 1 1 0 0 1 0 .696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1-19.876 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><h3>Transparency</h3><p>Clear roles, clear processes and no inflated promises.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section\"><div class=\"container timeline\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><span class=\"kicker\">The direction</span><h2>A platform designed to grow with the community.</h2></div><div class=\"timeline-item\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><span>0<!-- -->1</span><div><strong>Today</strong><p>Education-led website, inquiry and community learning.</p></div></div><div class=\"timeline-item\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><span>0<!-- -->2</span><div><strong>Next</strong><p>Articles, events, appointments and richer learning resources.</p></div></div><div class=\"timeline-item\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><span>0<!-- -->3</span><div><strong>Future</strong><p>Books, digital publications and a connected customer experience.</p></div></div></div></section></main><!--$--><!--